Dialogue: 1,0:24:18.41,0:24:19.99,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,既然兴起 Don’t stop
Dialogue: 1,0:24:19.99,0:24:22.97,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,坠入冷静的疯狂
Dialogue: 1,0:24:22.97,0:24:25.52,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,女神身边的败者
Dialogue: 1,0:24:25.72,0:24:27.25,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,狂吠 Give me back
Dialogue: 1,0:24:27.39,0:24:30.23,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,点燃冷却的呼吸
Dialogue: 1,0:24:30.23,0:24:34.66,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,如今手中的 Heart
Dialogue: 1,0:24:34.66,0:24:37.40,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,就要无法抑制
Dialogue: 1,0:24:37.40,0:24:39.96,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,无法 Playback 的 Deal
Dialogue: 1,0:24:39.96,0:24:42.90,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,邀请的危险视线
Dialogue: 1,0:24:42.90,0:24:45.41,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,Black or Red  登场
Dialogue: 1,0:24:45.41,0:24:49.00,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,决胜常需反其道而行
Dialogue: 1,0:24:49.30,0:24:52.73,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,玩弄作弊之人的正义微笑
Dialogue: 1,0:24:52.73,0:24:56.50,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,Ah  将一切掌握在这手中
Dialogue: 1,0:24:56.50,0:24:59.42,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,命运的赌局之上
Dialogue: 1,0:24:59.59,0:25:02.39,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,Bluff Bluff Bluff  在这手中
Dialogue: 1,0:25:02.39,0:25:04.88,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,想看我赌下的尊严？
Dialogue: 1,0:25:04.88,0:25:06.79,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,所谓 Bloody Heart 在此
Dialogue: 1,0:25:06.89,0:25:09.43,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,舍弃 Jack Queen King
Dialogue: 1,0:25:09.56,0:25:11.31,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,纵身于夜色
